<keyLead id="30907A400D4AFF8FFF42105B23DFCB97" pageId="11" pageNumber="553">
- Pronotum black with round red maculae (may be absent in 
<taxonomicName id="4C61A2F60D4AFF8FFCCF105B25C4CBB1" baseAuthorityName="Signoret" baseAuthorityYear="1854" box="[794,903,1136,1158]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Balacha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="553" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="distincta">
