<keyLead id="30907A400D4AFF8FFF42129123DFC9DA" pageId="11" pageNumber="553">- Forewings completely black or generally with three or four bluish-white transverse stripes, basalmost one and that over claval apex transcommissural; paraphyses absent; female pygofer and gonoplac apices round.............................. 6</keyLead>
