. 
<emphasis id="B91505670D4AFF8FFBFB13A2222EC8A9" box="[1070,1133,1928,1949]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="553">similis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFF0A4840D4AFF8FFBA613A223DFC8A9" author="Cavichioli, R. R. &amp; Sakakibara, A. M." box="[1139,1436,1928,1950]" pageId="11" pageNumber="553" pagination="279 - 291" refId="ref10710" refString="Cavichioli, R. R. &amp; Sakakibara, A. M. (1988) Especies brasileiras de Balacha Melichar, 1926 (Homoptera, Cicadellidae). Revista Brasileira de Entomologia, 32, 279 - 291." type="journal article" year="1988">Cavichioli &amp; Sakakibara, 1988</bibRefCitation>
